{"tid":564464,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"送巨型牌匾表白　勁似靈堂花牌　女主角拒愛：永遠單身","createTime":"2018-02-18T04:25:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-18T04:31:45.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"80a3304f81d1617a4f667b9fcd20ec0b114e7c54","tid":564464,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T04:25:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/159915/thumbnail/af0cf256668bb066e476ff4f6edcddbf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F159915%2Fthumbnail%2Faf0cf256668bb066e476ff4f6edcddbf.jpg&h=ca540428&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n情人節又到，如果覺得送花太普通，可以參考一名台灣男子送超大型「花牌」示愛，不過女生反應就&hellip;&hellip;閣下自理了。有台灣網民昨日在facebook群組「爆廢公社」上貼出一張照片，指在街邊看到一個寫着「情人節快樂」，但外形卻跟靈堂花牌非常相似，引起網民熱議，連女主角也親自現身回應事件，她一句「我永遠單身」，公開擊退了追求者。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1207765/xlarge/528d999153739eef956c304e3433b4e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1207765%2Fxlarge%2F528d999153739eef956c304e3433b4e1.jpg&h=7224af53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台灣網民在「爆廢公社」上載照片，表示路過板橋某巷弄時，看到這巨大的情人節禮物，上面寫着「祝王筠儀小姐情人節快樂，愛你的XX」。雖然花牌紅噹噹，但形狀相當「特別」，引起大量網民熱議，不少人都指有點像靈堂花牌，「覺得有點可怕」；又有網民笑稱禮物不錯，「隆重，盛大，莊嚴，有心」；不過最多人關注的卻是「男友可能活不久了」、「這是前男友嗎？」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1207767/xlarge/7f04b0b80545400332710d331e5305dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1207767%2Fxlarge%2F7f04b0b80545400332710d331e5305dd.jpg&h=55e774a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1207772/xlarge/a6ba66dd2aa5fb24ffa63ea9dac6d9fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1207772%2Fxlarge%2Fa6ba66dd2aa5fb24ffa63ea9dac6d9fd.jpg&h=4265df5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1207771/xlarge/45a79361090fc489c2a18c6dfd17064b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1207771%2Fxlarge%2F45a79361090fc489c2a18c6dfd17064b.jpg&h=edb06570&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1207774/xlarge/1f6d310f9b2620cf02a0d82bd3922aa6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1207774%2Fxlarge%2F1f6d310f9b2620cf02a0d82bd3922aa6.jpg&h=dfd27c25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1207773/xlarge/ba39fe9ead956abca9ccca66d889520b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1207773%2Fxlarge%2Fba39fe9ead956abca9ccca66d889520b.jpg&h=bf384fe1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1207828/xlarge/fa791c6d1611c131527bb674e3ee7bcd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1207828%2Fxlarge%2Ffa791c6d1611c131527bb674e3ee7bcd.jpg&h=20f41f75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n至於女主角「王筠儀」的名字，亦引起一眾網民興趣，人肉搜尋發現原來是有名氣的樂妃樂團團長。由於網上討論熱烈，女主角最終現身，還大方地和花圈合影，並上載到個人facebook，她承認這「較大張一點的卡片」是送給她的，但送這花牌的人「已經看不到晚上的月亮、明天的太陽了」，最後還狠狠地強調自己「永遠單身」，送花牌者，R.I.P。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：卡洛兒<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1/159915/-%E6%83%85%E4%BA%BA%E7%AF%80-%E9%80%81%E5%B7%A8%E5%9E%8B%E7%89%8C%E5%8C%BE%E8%A1%A8%E7%99%BD-%E5%8B%81%E4%BC%BC%E9%9D%88%E5%A0%82%E8%8A%B1%E7%89%8C-%E5%A5%B3%E4%B8%BB%E8%A7%92%E6%8B%92%E6%84%9B-%E6%B0%B8%E9%81%A0%E5%96%AE%E8%BA%AB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25A9%25B1%2F159915%2F-%25E6%2583%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25AF%2580-%25E9%2580%2581%25E5%25B7%25A8%25E5%259E%258B%25E7%2589%258C%25E5%258C%25BE%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E7%2599%25BD-%25E5%258B%2581%25E4%25BC%25BC%25E9%259D%2588%25E5%25A0%2582%25E8%258A%25B1%25E7%2589%258C-%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E8%25A7%2592%25E6%258B%2592%25E6%2584%259B-%25E6%25B0%25B8%25E9%2581%25A0%25E5%2596%25AE%25E8%25BA%25AB&d=ePnc8nuz0lVNRm5%2BXZzthzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=b6e84783\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1/159915/-%E6%83%85%E4%BA%BA%E7%AF%80-%E9%80%81%E5%B7%A8%E5%9E%8B%E7%89%8C%E5%8C%BE%E8%A1%A8%E7%99%BD-%E5%8B%81%E4%BC%BC%E9%9D%88%E5%A0%82%E8%8A%B1%E7%89%8C-%E5%A5%B3%E4%B8%BB%E8%A7%92%E6%8B%92%E6%84%9B-%E6%B0%B8%E9%81%A0%E5%96%AE%E8%BA%AB</a>"},{"pid":"6d262bef178de4b4ab4a45319d0fc82579ce9e14","tid":564464,"uid":35080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T04:25:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"294f3794518af81cbd85982d33971e1c5dffc926","tid":564464,"uid":52727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T04:25:59.000Z","msg":"雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"729e0d1dcedab4012dfc3c8a9448f3d7c440f332","tid":564464,"uid":27303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T04:31:45.000Z","msg":"好啊 唔好出黎害人"}]}